(Logo, you don't have to have Spears think all the right thoughts. 
It's like Dark Mouse used to be. You can be angry at Tamron all you 
want, but the chip prohibits you making thought into something else.)

Tamron

Tamron looked at his new soldier.

"Spears, eh? Nice name. For your orders, go pick up your boy friend 
and bring him to me. And nobody else move or I'll give the order for 
her to self-destruct herself!"
______________________________________________________________________
Starscream

Starscream started to get impatient.

"Where is Zardus? The future of the Alliance hangs in the balance."
______________________________________________________________________
Fliq

As the shuttle was racing across space heading back to Earth, Fliq 
turned to look at Ramulus.

"Still feel sick?"
______________________________________________________________________
Vulois

Vulois kept channelign energy into Child. He than focused for a bit, 
and sent one huge pile of energy at once. This caused a special 
psycic link between the two. Vulois sent an image of himself into 
Child's head. Vulois was infront of a door, and he had a key in his 
hand.

"Tell me the answer and i'll give you the key." he said in Child's 
mind.
